high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is next to the fork.
Turn left and walk to past the table, then turn right and left and go to the sink in front of you.
Place the lettuce in the sink and turn on the water.
Take the lettuce out of the sink then turn to the left and walk straight until you reach the counter.
Place the washed lettuce in front of the tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the washed lettuce on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Bring the lettuce to the counter on the left next to the coffee machine.
Put the lettuce on the counter in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put cleaned lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and face the lettuce on the white table.
Pick the lettuce up off of the white table.
Turn and walk to stand in front of the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, turn the water on and then off and take the lettuce out of the sink.
Go left and stand in front of the sink in front of the coffee maker.
Set the lettuce on the counter to the right of the oven.
anns.task_desc: Put washed lettuce on the counter.
